Class SwiftFileSystemOptionsRegistar

    @AutoService(value=org.apache.beam.sdk.options.PipelineOptionsRegistrar.class)
public class SwiftFileSystemOptionsRegistar
extends Object
implements PipelineOptionsRegistrar
    Register SwiftFileSystemOptions, allowing SwiftFileSystemOptions to be shown in Beam help messages.

    PipelineOptionsFactory.initializeRegistry() employs ServiceLoader to load all registered PipelineOptions.
